Welcome
-------

WeirdDices is a small android app that emulate RPG dices rolling. Dedicated to 
those that need a handy Zocchi Set but are unable to load themself with strange
polyhedrons.

Build
-----

You will need an android SDK. This app was developped with Android 2.1 in mind.
You may have to create an empty ant.properties file.

Copying
-------

Free use of this software is granted under the terms of the GNU General Public 
License (GPL). For details see the files `COPYING` included with the WeirdDices
distribution.
